      "level": 2,
      "text": "Inspection"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "Check for scratches on the cover inner surface and internal diameter of the gear ports.\nCheck for smooth movement of lubrication valve, and scratches on sliding surfaces.\nCheck smooth operation of pump gears.\nEnsure components are clean and free from foreign matter.\nReplace the oil pump as an assembly, if necessary.",
      "style": "normal"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Assembly"
    },
    {
      "block_type": "prose",
      "text": "Apply ATF to all moving parts during assembly.\nTighten the bolts evenly.\nCheck shaft rotates smoothly.",
      "style": "normal"
    },
